name: Golden Pineapple - Audio Trip VR
description:
Audio Trip VR is a virtual reality dance game developed by Kinemotik Studios. This is a fly-through of the game environment for Golden Pineapple, which was the track released for the game's launch on Quest in May 2021. The choreography & stage have been removed to fully display the environment as seen in the game.

Music by Tolan
Visual from Audio Trip - twitter @AudioTripVR

Duration: 02:41
